We can use {osrm} to calculate isochrones



iso &lt;- osrmIsochrone(location, breaks = seq(0, 60, 15), res = 10)

isochrone_ids &lt;- unique(iso$id)

pal &lt;- colorFactor(
  viridisLite::viridis(length(isochrone_ids)),
  isochrone_ids
)

